## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **clascoterone Winlevi 2020** = first FDA topical AR antagonist for acne. 성인 + 청소년 12+ both sexes 적응증. 이전에 oral spironolactone 만성 hormonal acne 1L off-label 만 가능했던 것을 topical 로 옮긴 paradigm shift. quantum-VQE 의 AR pocket + topical penetration 이 직접 fit.
2. **trifarotene Aklief 2019** = first FDA RAR-γ selective topical retinoid. 이전 tretinoin/adapalene/tazarotene = pan-RAR or RAR-β/γ. RAR-γ 가 sebocyte 와 follicular keratinocyte 에 dominant. truncal acne 적응증 확장. quantum-VQE 의 RAR isoform-selective leverage.
3. **sarecycline Seysara 2018** = first FDA narrow-spectrum oral tetracycline. C. acnes 선택적 + GI microbiome 보존. doxycycline + minocycline broad-spectrum 의 next mechanism. quantum-VQE 의 30S ribosome narrow-spectrum binding modeling.
4. **topical minocycline foam Amzeeq 2019 + Zilxi 2020 (rosacea)** = 첫 topical minocycline. oral systemic AE 회피 + foam vehicle penetration. quantum-VQE 의 topical 결합 vehicle modeling.
5. **isotretinoin 1982 + iPLEDGE program** = first severe acne 만성 disease-modifying. 임신 contraindication + 정신건강 모니터 (cross-women_obgyn + psychiatric). 양자-VQE 의 RAR pan-binding + 4년 long-term remission paradigm.
6. **adapalene OTC 2016 + Epiduo 2008** = OTC 시대 + fixed-dose combo paradigm. patient compliance 향상. K-pharma 의 manufacturing + 식약처 approval pathway crosstalk.
7. **spironolactone off-label 1L 성인 여성 hormonal acne** = AR antagonist oral 만성 대안. PCOS + 만성 endocrine cross-link. quantum-VQE 의 AR oral pocket vs topical (clascoterone) 비교.
8. **olumacostat glasaretil ACC1 inhibitor Phase 3 fail** = sebum-modulating mechanism 의 첫 Phase 3 fail. lipid synthesis modulation 의 efficacy ceiling. quantum-VQE 의 ACC1 pocket failure analysis.
9. **K-acne 임상 framework + 식약처 + K-cosmetic + K-aesthetic_dermatology** = 한국 청소년 + 성인 여성 acne paradigm + K-beauty 가 OTC + Rx + cosmetic 경계. cross-k_pharma_industry + aesthetic_dermatology.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, acne 임상 의미 한정.

